{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":95,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"住口！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":15,"line_start":2,"line_end":2},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"你要我住口？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":4,"line_end":4},{"speaker":"char_leng_da","speaker_name":"冷大","listener":null,"text":"正是要你住口。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":6,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"你……你连谁是敌人、谁是朋友都分不出么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":8,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_leng_da","speaker_name":"冷大","listener":null,"text":"我宁可有他这样的仇敌，也不愿有你这样的朋友。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":10,"line_end":10}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_jin_bu_huan","name":"金不换","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"金不换，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":1,"line_end":95,"text":"第十四回　初脱虎口\n金不换语意刻薄，朱七七正要发作，冷大已转身怒叱道：\"住口！\"\n\n金不换怔了一怔，道：\"你要我住口？\"\n\n冷大道：\"正是要你住口。\"\n\n金不换道：\"你……你连谁是敌人、谁是朋友都分不"}]},{"id":"char_leng_da","name":"冷大","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"冷大，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":1,"line_end":95,"text":"第十四回　初脱虎口\n金不换语意刻薄，朱七七正要发作，冷大已转身怒叱道：\"住口！\"\n\n金不换怔了一怔，道：\"你要我住口？\"\n\n冷大道：\"正是要你住口。\"\n\n金不换道：\"你……你连谁是敌人、谁是朋友都分不"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":96,"line_end":190,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"李兄且看这一战两人是谁胜谁负？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":96,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"李公之言，实是中肯之极。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":110,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"那……又当怎生是好？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":116,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"两人相争，优胜劣败，本是丝毫不能勉强之事，只是……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":118,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"不错，除此之外，还有何策？","tone":"苦笑","chapter":15,"line_start":124,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"但李公昔年受创之后，至今功力仍未恢复，却不知能否……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"不瞒金兄，在下若与此人动手，更是败多胜少。","tone":"无奈","chapter":15,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"此人武功实是深不可测，除非他连经剧战之后，气力不济，否则……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":134,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"此人功力，在下倒略知一二。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":136,"line_end":136},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"请教。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":138,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"若真的如此，只怕……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":144,"line_end":144},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"只怕天法大师也难以取胜，是么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":146,"line_end":146},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"这……唉！","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":156,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"这……除非……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":162,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"除非怎样？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":164,"line_end":164},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"除非你我一齐出手。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":166,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"怎样……怎样……","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":176,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"好，就是如此。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":178,"line_end":178}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_jin_bu_huan","name":"金不换","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"金不换，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":96,"line_end":190,"text":"金不换悄声道：\"李兄且看这一战两人是谁胜谁负？\"\n\n李长青沉吟半晌，苦笑道：\"若论武功之强韧，意志之坚忍，交手经验之丰富，临敌判断之冷静，他两人可说是棋逢敌手，不相上下！\n\n\"\n\n金不换颔首道：\"不错"}]},{"id":"char_li_chang_qing","name":"李长青","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"李长青，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":96,"line_end":190,"text":"金不换悄声道：\"李兄且看这一战两人是谁胜谁负？\"\n\n李长青沉吟半晌，苦笑道：\"若论武功之强韧，意志之坚忍，交手经验之丰富，临敌判断之冷静，他两人可说是棋逢敌手，不相上下！\n\n\"\n\n金不换颔首道：\"不错"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":191,"line_end":280,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"大家一齐上呀，先将这两人收拾下来再说。","tone":"厉声","chapter":15,"line_start":198,"line_end":198},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"莫要回头，莫要上他的当。","tone":"厉声","chapter":15,"line_start":210,"line_end":210},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"你……你将他怎么样了？","tone":"厉声","chapter":15,"line_start":218,"line_end":218},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"恶贼，你……你要怎样？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":224,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"我要以他的性命，换一个人的性命。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":226,"line_end":226},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"做梦？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":15,"line_start":232,"line_end":232},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"正是如此。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":238,"line_end":238},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"他如此做了，岂非弄巧成拙……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":242,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"你笑什么？你还笑得出？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":246,"line_end":246},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"你瞧瞧这是什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":248,"line_end":248},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"那是什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":256,"line_end":256},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"这便是解药。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":258,"line_end":258},{"speaker":"char_li_chang_qing","speaker_name":"李长青","listener":null,"text":"解药，你……你要吞下去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":260,"line_end":260},{"speaker":"char_jin_bu_huan","speaker_name":"金不换","listener":null,"text":"那……那你究竟要怎样？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":280,"line_end":280}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_jin_bu_huan","name":"金不换","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"金不换，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":191,"line_end":280,"text":"\n金无望身形凌空一转，已掠到朱七七身侧，口中厉声道：\"金不换，我早已算定你有此一着，是以始终分心留意看你，你若想要害我，还差得远哩。\n\n\"\n\n众人一听他方才根本未曾将全部心神都用来对付冷大，冷大已是不"}]},{"id":"char_zhu_qi_qi","name":"朱七七","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"朱七七，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":191,"line_end":280,"text":"\n金无望身形凌空一转，已掠到朱七七身侧，口中厉声道：\"金不换，我早已算定你有此一着，是以始终分心留意看你，你若想要害我，还差得远哩。\n\n\"\n\n众人一听他方才根本未曾将全部心神都用来对付冷大，冷大已是不"}]},{"id":"char_jin_wu_wang","name":"金无望","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"金无望，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":191,"line_end":280,"text":"\n金无望身形凌空一转，已掠到朱七七身侧，口中厉声道：\"金不换，我早已算定你有此一着，是以始终分心留意看你，你若想要害我，还差得远哩。\n\n\"\n\n众人一听他方才根本未曾将全部心神都用来对付冷大，冷大已是不"}]},{"id":"char_li_chang_qing","name":"李长青","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"李长青，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":191,"line_end":280,"text":"\n金无望身形凌空一转，已掠到朱七七身侧，口中厉声道：\"金不换，我早已算定你有此一着，是以始终分心留意看你，你若想要害我，还差得远哩。\n\n\"\n\n众人一听他方才根本未曾将全部心神都用来对付冷大，冷大已是不"}]