{"segment":5,"line_start":381,"line_end":490,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"少啰嗦！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":15,"line_start":400,"line_end":400},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"有什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":416,"line_end":416},{"speaker":"char_dian_huo","speaker_name":"店伙","listener":null,"text":"小店做的是南北'口味，面饭都有，阳春面、肉丝面……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":418,"line_end":418},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"好，来碗肉丝面吧。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":420,"line_end":420},{"speaker":"char_dian_huo","speaker_name":"店伙","listener":null,"text":"好，这就送来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":422,"line_end":422},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"不得了，不得了……打死人啦……打死人啦……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":430,"line_end":430},{"speaker":"char_wang_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"王掌柜","listener":null,"text":"方才俺正和猪肉铺的李胖子聊天，说晌午俺店里来了两个稀罕客人，那女的可真是标致，男的却是三分有点像鬼，七分不大像人，就好像一朵鲜花插在牛粪上似的，俺将李胖子说笑了，俺也笑了，哪知就在这当口，突然冲将来一条野汉子，就将俺揍了一顿，俺……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":440,"line_end":440},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"再说呀。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":448,"line_end":448},{"speaker":"char_wang_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"王掌柜","listener":null,"text":"俺说……说……说……说……说不出了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":450,"line_end":450},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你说谁像鬼？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":452,"line_end":452},{"speaker":"char_wang_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"王掌柜","listener":null,"text":"俺……俺说自己……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":454,"line_end":454},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"方才揍你的人是何模样？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":456,"line_end":456},{"speaker":"char_wang_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"王掌柜","listener":null,"text":"浓眉毛，大眼睛，俺也瞧不……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":458,"line_end":458},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"熊猫儿……熊猫儿……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":464,"line_end":464},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"但……但你怎会到这里来的？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":480,"line_end":480},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"来找你的……你呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":482,"line_end":482},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"我也是来找你的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":484,"line_end":484},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"真的？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":486,"line_end":486},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"走，去喝一杯。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":488,"line_end":488}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_zhu_qi_qi","name":"朱七七","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"朱七七，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":381,"line_end":490,"text":"\n她低语道：\"我走这条路，又不是去找沈浪，我是去找……去找别人的，张三李四，王二麻子，我谁都可以找，我无论去求什么人帮我的忙，那人都会帮我的，那么，我就可以要他们来救金无望。\n\n\"\n\n其实她自己也知道"}]},{"id":"char_dian_huo","name":"店伙","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"店伙，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":381,"line_end":490,"text":"\n她低语道：\"我走这条路，又不是去找沈浪，我是去找……去找别人的，张三李四，王二麻子，我谁都可以找，我无论去求什么人帮我的忙，那人都会帮我的，那么，我就可以要他们来救金无望。\n\n\"\n\n其实她自己也知道"}]},{"id":"char_wang_zhang_gui","name":"王掌柜","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"王掌柜，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":381,"line_end":490,"text":"\n她低语道：\"我走这条路，又不是去找沈浪，我是去找……去找别人的，张三李四，王二麻子，我谁都可以找，我无论去求什么人帮我的忙，那人都会帮我的，那么，我就可以要他们来救金无望。\n\n\"\n\n其实她自己也知道"}]},{"id":"char_xiong_mao_er","name":"熊猫儿","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"熊猫儿，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":381,"line_end":490,"text":"\n她低语道：\"我走这条路，又不是去找沈浪，我是去找……去找别人的，张三李四，王二麻子，我谁都可以找，我无论去求什么人帮我的忙，那人都会帮我的，那么，我就可以要他们来救金无望。\n\n\"\n\n其实她自己也知道"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":6,"line_start":491,"line_end":580,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"不想你居然还记挂着我，还来找我。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":498,"line_end":498},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"不知沈……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":514,"line_end":514},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"你可是要问沈浪？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":516,"line_end":516},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"谁问他？王八蛋才问他。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":518,"line_end":518},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"这种坏蛋，你等他干什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":526,"line_end":526},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"我可不是等他，我是等你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":528,"line_end":528},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"真的？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":530,"line_end":530},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你倒了霉，才会认得他。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":536,"line_end":536},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"王怜花虽然问得起劲，我却懒得理他，但有他在一旁，我又不好意思走，幸好那时已有救星来了……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":538,"line_end":538},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"是沈……是谁？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":540,"line_end":540},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"那人不是沈浪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":542,"line_end":542},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"我又没有问他，鬼才……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":544,"line_end":544},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"你问他本是应当的，你何必……","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":546,"line_end":546},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你可认得他？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":562,"line_end":562},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"那人说些什么，你可曾听到？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":568,"line_end":568},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"我堂堂男子汉，怎会偷听别人的话？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":570,"line_end":570},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你呀……你的可爱处，就在这些地方，从来不会假正经……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":574,"line_end":574}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_zhu_qi_qi","name":"朱七七","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"朱七七，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":491,"line_end":580,"text":"\n开畅，早已浑然忘了什么男女礼教之防。\n\n但别人却如见着瘟神，见着怪物一般，远远就躲了开去，那位王掌柜，更是逃得不知去向。\n\n熊猫儿与朱七七却更是得其所哉，自管在店里坐下，没有人招待他们，他们就喝自己"}]},{"id":"char_xiong_mao_er","name":"熊猫儿","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"熊猫儿，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":491,"line_end":580,"text":"\n开畅，早已浑然忘了什么男女礼教之防。\n\n但别人却如见着瘟神，见着怪物一般，远远就躲了开去，那位王掌柜，更是逃得不知去向。\n\n熊猫儿与朱七七却更是得其所哉，自管在店里坐下，没有人招待他们，他们就喝自己"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":7,"line_start":581,"line_end":690,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"每个鬼鬼祟祟的人，都是这样的，沈……沈浪还不是如此……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":582,"line_end":582},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"我……我相信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":586,"line_end":586},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"你可知他这是为什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":612,"line_end":612},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"谁知道！鬼才知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":614,"line_end":614},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"都像你我这样，可也天下大乱了。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":620,"line_end":620},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你这人真好，竟还在为他说话……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":626,"line_end":626},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"想你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":644,"line_end":644},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"我不寂寞，有个人陪着……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":654,"line_end":654},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"不好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":656,"line_end":656},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"什么事不好了？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":660,"line_end":660},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你听到了么？快走呀。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":668,"line_end":668},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"你见着我，真的高兴？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":680,"line_end":680},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"真的……真的……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":682,"line_end":682},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"咱们走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":684,"line_end":684},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"真是个小孩子……","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":686,"line_end":686}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_zhu_qi_qi","name":"朱七七","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"朱七七，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":581,"line_end":690,"text":"\n朱七七道：\"每个鬼鬼祟祟的人，都是这样的，沈……沈浪还不是如此……\"脸上忽然一红，垂首道：\"我可不是在想他，只不过拿他做个比喻。\n\n\"\n\n熊猫儿道：\"我……我相信。\"\n\n朱七七又道：\"你们与沈浪接近"}]},{"id":"char_xiong_mao_er","name":"熊猫儿","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"熊猫儿，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":581,"line_end":690,"text":"\n朱七七道：\"每个鬼鬼祟祟的人，都是这样的，沈……沈浪还不是如此……\"脸上忽然一红，垂首道：\"我可不是在想他，只不过拿他做个比喻。\n\n\"\n\n熊猫儿道：\"我……我相信。\"\n\n朱七七又道：\"你们与沈浪接近"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":8,"line_start":691,"line_end":800,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"不对。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":694,"line_end":694},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"什么不对？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":696,"line_end":696},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"这足迹在兜着圈子，只怕又是你们……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":698,"line_end":698},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"是我们的，只因……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":700,"line_end":700},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"就在这里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":706,"line_end":706},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"这就是你们方才动手之处？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":708,"line_end":708},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"不错……但他们却已走了，莫非金无望已被……已被他们所擒……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":710,"line_end":710},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"你瞧那里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":712,"line_end":712},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"如此说来他……他莫非已遇害了么？","tone":"颤声","chapter":15,"line_start":722,"line_end":722},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"难道你瞧不出？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":740,"line_end":740},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"我……我……好像……有些……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":742,"line_end":742},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"好，我认输了，我瞧不出。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":746,"line_end":746},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"你仔细瞧瞧看，只因你还没有捉摸到观察事物的方法……","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":748,"line_end":748},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你捉摸到了，你厉害，你倒是说呀。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":750,"line_end":750},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"你瞧，这个足印最大，想见此人身材最是魁伟，而这几人之中，身材最最魁伟的便是……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":752,"line_end":752},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"不错，这足印是连天云的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":754,"line_end":754},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"天法大师！这是天法那老和尚的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":760,"line_end":760},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"但还有三个足印，我又看不出了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":772,"line_end":772},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"不错，不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":788,"line_end":788},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"不错……不错……","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":798,"line_end":798}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiong_mao_er","name":"熊猫儿","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"熊猫儿，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":691,"line_end":800,"text":"\n到了荒僻处，突又多了一人足迹，便是那时跟在他们身后的金不换所留了。\n\n熊猫儿追着这足迹奔了许久，突然住足道：\"不对。\"\n\n朱七七道：\"什么不对？\"\n\n熊猫儿道：\"这足迹在兜着圈子，只怕又是你们……\""}]},{"id":"char_zhu_qi_qi","name":"朱七七","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"朱七七，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":691,"line_end":800,"text":"\n到了荒僻处，突又多了一人足迹，便是那时跟在他们身后的金不换所留了。\n\n熊猫儿追着这足迹奔了许久，突然住足道：\"不对。\"\n\n朱七七道：\"什么不对？\"\n\n熊猫儿道：\"这足迹在兜着圈子，只怕又是你们……\""}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":9,"line_start":801,"line_end":900,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你这小猫猫，你真是越来越聪明了。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":804,"line_end":804},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"其实我这观察事物之法，多是自沈浪那里学来的，他……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":808,"line_end":808},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"你不愿听，以后我……我再也不说就是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":818,"line_end":818},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"再说……再说你是什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":820,"line_end":820},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"再说就是王八蛋。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":822,"line_end":822},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"好，脚印都分出了，然后呢？","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":824,"line_end":824},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"还有呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":830,"line_end":830},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"这些足印，足尖向外，显然是他们离去时留下的，但这其中，却少了金无望的脚印……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":832,"line_end":832},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"如此看来，莫非他已被人制住，抬着走了？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":15,"line_start":834,"line_end":834},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"想来只怕是如此的了。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":15,"line_start":836,"line_end":836},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"这些脚印，都比他们来时深得多了，显见他们的气力也耗损了不少，尤其是连天云和冷大……","tone":"沉声","chapter":15,"line_start":842,"line_end":842},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"求求你，帮我去救他好么？","tone":"颤声","chapter":15,"line_start":860,"line_end":860},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"我……我……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":862,"line_end":862},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"我世上的亲人，只有一个你，你难道忍心……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":864,"line_end":864},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":866,"line_end":866},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"上山呀，发什么怔！","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":882,"line_end":882},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"莫非……莫非他们要将他带到山上害死？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":890,"line_end":890}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_zhu_qi_qi","name":"朱七七","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"朱七七，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":801,"line_end":900,"text":"\n\"\n\n朱七七笑道：\"你这小猫猫，你真是越来越聪明了。\"突然伸出手来，在熊猫儿面颊轻轻拧了一下。\n\n这\"小猫猫\"三个字，当真有说不出的亲密，说不出的爱娇，那轻轻一拧，更是令人灵魂上天。\n\n熊猫儿痴痴地"}]},{"id":"char_xiong_mao_er","name":"熊猫儿","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"熊猫儿，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":801,"line_end":900,"text":"\n\"\n\n朱七七笑道：\"你这小猫猫，你真是越来越聪明了。\"突然伸出手来，在熊猫儿面颊轻轻拧了一下。\n\n这\"小猫猫\"三个字，当真有说不出的亲密，说不出的爱娇，那轻轻一拧，更是令人灵魂上天。\n\n熊猫儿痴痴地"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":10,"line_start":901,"line_end":1000,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"奇怪……奇怪……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":912,"line_end":912},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"你猜出了？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":918,"line_end":918},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"结果是怎么样了？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":924,"line_end":924},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"呀，果然好计。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":930,"line_end":930},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"为什么？这次为什么就不一样？","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":936,"line_end":936},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"那古墓之事，我们所知虽不多，但想来必是些诡秘的勾当，自然要装神弄鬼，故布疑阵，而天法大师这些人……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":938,"line_end":938},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"这些人难道就是好人么？","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":940,"line_end":940},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"这……我还是不知道。","tone":"无奈","chapter":15,"line_start":952,"line_end":952},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"熊猫儿道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":956,"line_end":956},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"救命呀……救命呀……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":960,"line_end":960},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"我……我已要掉下去啦，哪位仁人君子，来拉我一把吧，我一辈子也忘不了你老人家的好处……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":966,"line_end":966},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"幸好这人命不该绝，还未掉下去，我们都恰巧在山上……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":970,"line_end":970},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"且慢，我瞧此事……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":976,"line_end":976},{"speaker":"char_xiong_mao_er","speaker_name":"熊猫儿","listener":null,"text":"我瞧此事总有些……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":982,"line_end":982},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"好，我去救他，你在这里等着。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":990,"line_end":990},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"用力……快……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":992,"line_end":992}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiong_mao_er","name":"熊猫儿","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"熊猫儿，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":901,"line_end":1000,"text":"\n两人显然都没有什么主意，只有上山瞧个明白。\n\n但山路崎岖，有的岩石、藤草间，积雪甚少；有的地方雪花被山岩挡住，地上根本就无积雪。\n\n于是他们追查足迹，便无方才那么容易。\n\n两人走走停停，张张望望，到"}]},{"id":"char_zhu_qi_qi","name":"朱七七","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"朱七七，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":901,"line_end":1000,"text":"\n两人显然都没有什么主意，只有上山瞧个明白。\n\n但山路崎岖，有的岩石、藤草间，积雪甚少；有的地方雪花被山岩挡住，地上根本就无积雪。\n\n于是他们追查足迹，便无方才那么容易。\n\n两人走走停停，张张望望，到"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":11,"line_start":1001,"line_end":1096,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你这恶贼，还我熊猫儿的命来。","tone":"厉声","chapter":15,"line_start":1010,"line_end":1010},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"好孩子，你敢和我动手？","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":1014,"line_end":1014},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"好孩子，难为你还认得我。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":1026,"line_end":1026},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你……你是……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":1028,"line_end":1028},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你……你……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":1036,"line_end":1036},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"姑姑对你那么好，替你穿衣服，喂你吃饭，你却还是要跑走，你这个没良心的，","tone":"柔声","chapter":15,"line_start":1038,"line_end":1038},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"求……求……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":1042,"line_end":1042},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你滚……滚……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":1048,"line_end":1048},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"你怎么能叫姑姑滚，姑姑这正要带你走了，替你换上好看的衣服，喂你吃些好吃的东西……","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":1050,"line_end":1050},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你过来，我打死你。","tone":"厉声","chapter":15,"line_start":1054,"line_end":1054},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你还是乖乖的……","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":1060,"line_end":1060},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"放开我……放开我……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":1070,"line_end":1070},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"小宝贝，我怎舍得放开你？","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":1072,"line_end":1072},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"我杀了你，你怎会感激我？你这是在说笑吧？","tone":"轻笑","chapter":15,"line_start":1094,"line_end":1094},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"真的……真的……真的……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":1096,"line_end":1096}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_zhu_qi_qi","name":"朱七七","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"朱七七，武林中人","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":1001,"line_end":1096,"text":"\n这变化委实太过突然。\n\n朱七七如遭雷轰电击，整个人都怔在当地。\n\n只听熊猫儿惨叫之声，余音未了，断崖下却已有狞笑之声发出，一条人影，随着笑声翻了上来，\n\n这时天时已晚，沉沉暮色中，只见此人身穿大棉袄"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
